summary: This is a new world I have created. It is not finished, but please tell me how it looks so far. I am hoping to make a whole world and quest line. To get to Kayward, check outside Solitude, there should be a new area on the map. Ideas for the world are always welcome. :)
descriptionHtml: This is a new world I have created. It is not finished, but please tell me how it looks so far. I am hoping to make a whole world and quest line. To get to Kayward, check outside Solitude, there should be a new area on the map. -- Another thing I like about this world, you start of in the town Kayward Hope, and there are fully functional guards that will arrest. Thanks! Tell me what you think so far. Ideas are always welcome! :)
